---
// FAQ section with accordion
---

<section id="faq" class="section faq">
  <div class="container" style="max-width: 800px;">
    <div class="text-center mb-20">
      <h2 class="section-title">Common Questions</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-list">
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>
          Is it really free?
        </summary>
        <p>
          Yes. No trial period, no catch. The Free plan is free forever. The Pro plan exists for those who want analytics and to remove the Noko badge.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>
          Why is it free?
        </summary>
        <p>
          Noko is a project by Jon Labs, a web studio based in Geneva. We built it for our clients, then realized it could be useful for everyone.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>
          What's the difference with Linktree?
        </summary>
        <p>
          We keep the essentials. Links, customization, it's the same. What we add: Free branded QR code, "Add to Contacts" button, and a Pro price that is 2x cheaper.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>
          Can I migrate from Linktree?
        </summary>
        <p>
          In 2 minutes. You create your page, copy your links, change the URL in your bio. That's it.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>
          Where is my data stored?
        </summary>
        <p>
          On servers in Switzerland.
        </p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .faq-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .faq-item {
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .faq-item:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .faq-item[open] {
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
    background: var(--color-surface);
  }

  .faq-item summary {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text);
    list-style: none;
    position: relative;
    padding-right: 2rem;
  }

  .faq-item summary::-webkit-details-marker {
    display: none;
  }

  .faq-item summary::after {
    content: '+';
    position: absolute;
    right: 0;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .faq-item[open] summary::after {
    content: 'âˆ’';
  }

  .faq-item p {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    animation: slideDown 0.2s ease-out;
  }

  @keyframes slideDown {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-5px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
</style>

<script>
  // Optional: Accordion behavior - close others when one opens
  const faqItems = document.querySelectorAll('.faq-item');

  faqItems.forEach(item => {
    item.addEventListener('toggle', () => {
      if ((item as HTMLDetailsElement).open) {
        faqItems.forEach(otherItem => {
          if (otherItem !== item && (otherItem as HTMLDetailsElement).open) {
            (otherItem as HTMLDetailsElement).open = false;
          }
        });
      }
    });
  });
</script>